{"id": "xos043", "name": "Multi_File_X043", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Student A"], "content": "Shannon, bye-bye~ See you next week.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Okay! See you next week!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "Engine sounds"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon, want a ride?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Dad!? What are you doing here!?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Jeez, stop picking me up with the admins' car!\nMy classmates all laugh at me for this.\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "I'm worried about you. The security in this area has been getting worse and worse too...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Isn't that your fault, for not doing your job well?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Haha... well, that I am guilty of.\nHowever, I'm relieved to see that you have many friends at school.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "I'm already far passed that age where I get bullied all the time. Dad, don't just remember things from that time. I'm not a child anymore.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Speaking of which, things back then were truly... got to thank Simon for that. Do you still see him?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Yep! He's doing great. He often invites me to see their practices or performances. Their band is really awesome, and all the members are really fun people! Especially Sis Cherry! It looks like their da... ah!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Da...?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "N... Nothing! All in all, dad should go listen to their next performance too!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "I don't have that kind of time... Besides, isn't it just some noisy music?\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["CP_velkinta", "Play Music"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Hey! What are you doing!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Ah, what a coincidence. I turn on your music player and the first song just so happens to be \"noisy music\"~\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "If it wasn't for the guitar you gifted him, he wouldn't have gone into music in the first place. Say, isn't it about time you two stop giving each other the silent treatment?\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "... Hmph, if he wants to come back, he can come back whenever he wants.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Here we go again~ Who would want to live with you if you have that attitude...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "Brakes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Wahh! W-what's the matter!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "......!!\nShannon... get out the car.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "It's that guy...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "Dad...?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Get out the car, now! Listen carefully; don't do anything else, go straight back home, got it?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "Car Door"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "Shannonちゃんバイバーイ！\nまた来週！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "うん！バイバイ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "車のエンジン"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon、乗るか？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お父さん！ここで何してるの！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "もー！管理局の車で迎えに来ないでよね！\nみんなに噂されちゃうんだから。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "心配なんだ。\nここら辺の治安は年々悪くなってるからな……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お父さんがちゃんと仕事してないから？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "はは……そうだな。認めよう。\nでも、学校にたくさん友達がいるみたいでよかった。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "もう、私そんないつまでもいじめられてるだけの子供じゃないよ？\nお父さんはいっつもあの時のことばっかり思い出すんだもん。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "あの時は……本当にSimonに感謝しないとな。\n最近会ったか？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "うん！元気そうだったよ。\n私、よくお兄ちゃんの練習とかライブ見に行くんだ。\nお兄ちゃんのバンドすごいんだよ。\nメンバーのみんなも面白い人たちばっかりだし！\nあ！Cherryさんはね！お兄ちゃんと……あ！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Simonとなんだ？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "な……なんでもない！\nとにかく！今度一緒に聴きに行こうね！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "父さんにそんな時間はないな……\nどうせただうるさいだけの曲だろう？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["CP_velkinta", "音楽再生"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "うわ！急に何をするんだ！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "あ、偶然！\nつけた瞬間にちょうど「うるさいだけの曲」が流れちゃった。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お父さんがギターなんかプレゼントしなければ、お兄ちゃんだって音楽に興味持ってなかったと思うよ？\nもうそろそろ、その冷戦も終わりにしない？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……ふん、帰って来たいならいつでも帰ってくればいいだろう。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "またそんなこと言って～\nそんなんじゃ誰もお父さんと一緒に住みたいなんて……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "ブレーキ"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "きゃっ！な、なに！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……！！\nShannon……降りなさい。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "あいつ……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "お父さん……？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "降りなさい！いいか？まっすぐ家に帰るんだ。\n分かったな？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "車のドア"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "Shannon，拜拜～下週見喔。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "嗯！下週見！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "汽車引擎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon，要搭便車嗎？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "爸！？你在這裡做什麼啊！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真是的，別再開管理局的車來載我了啦！同學都會笑耶。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "我不放心啊，最近這一區治安也越來越差了……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "那不是都是因為爸沒做好工作？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "哈哈……好吧，我認罪。\n不過，太好了，看到妳在學校有那麼多朋友。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "我早就過了那個老是被欺負的年紀啦，爸別老是只記得那時候的事，我不是小孩子了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "說起來當時真的……要感謝 Simon 啊。\n最近還有再見到他嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "嗯！他很好，也常常找我去看他們練團或表演；他們的樂團很棒，團員也都是很有趣的人喔！特別是 Cherry 姐！他們好像在交……啊！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "交？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "沒……沒事！總之下次爸也去聽吧！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "我哪有那麼多閒時間啊……不就是些吵死人的音樂而已嗎？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["CP_velkinta", "音樂播放"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "哇！妳幹嘛！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "啊，好巧喔，一打開就是吵死人的音樂耶。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "要不是你送他吉他，他也不會跑去玩樂團囉。我說你們也差不多該解除冷戰了吧？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……哼，他如果想回來隨時可以回來啊。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "又來了～你這個態度誰想跟你住……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "煞車"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哇！怎、怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……！！\nShannon……下車。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "是那傢伙……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "爸……？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "快下車！聽好，直接回家，知道嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "車門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["학생 A"], "content": "Shannon, 안녕~ 다음 주에 봐~\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "응~ 바이바이!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "엔진음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon, 타고 갈래?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "아빠?? 뭐야? 여기서 뭐 하고 있었어!?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "아 진짜! 관리국 차로 데리러 오지 말랬지! 애들이 놀린단 말이야!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "걱정돼서 그러지.\n이 근처 치안은 해마다 나빠지고 있어서 말이야.....\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "그건 아빠가 제대로 일을 안 해서 그런 거겠지~\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "하하하......그래~ 인정하마.\n그래도 학교에 친구들이 많이 있는 것 같아 다행이구나.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "언제적 얘길 하는 거야! \n아빠는 꼭 기억해도 그때 모습만 기억하고 있어! 이젠 나도 예전처럼 괴롭힘만 당하던 그런 아이가 아니라구!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "그때는 정말... Simon에게도 많이 고마워하고 있단다. 요즘 만난 적 있니?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "응! 잘 지내는 것 같던데?\n자주 오빠 밴드 연습이나 라이브도 보러가곤 하거든. \n오빠네 밴드 진짜 대단해!\n멤버들도 엄청 웃긴 사람들이고!\n아! 특히 Cherry 언니! 오빠랑 사귀는 것 같던... 아 참!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "사귄다고?\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "아... 아무것도 아니야! 어쨌든 아빠도 나중에 가서 들어봐!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "아빠가 그럴 시간이 어딨니...그리고...\n분명 또 엄청 시끄럽기만한 음악이겠지.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["CP_velkinta", "음악 재생"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon ! ? 뭐하는 거니!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "앗~? 이런 우연이?\n음악을 재생한 순간에 마침 '시끄럽기만한 음악'이 흘러나와버렸네~?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "애초에 아빠가 기타를 선물해주지 않았으면, 오빠도 밴드 같은 거 안 했을 걸?\n그리고 이제 둘 다... 서로 풀 때도 됐잖아.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "...흥... 돌아오고 싶은 마음이 생기면 그때 돌아오든가 하겠지.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "또 그런다~!\n아빠가 자꾸 이런 태도인데 누가 아빠랑 같이 살고 싶겠어...!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "브레이크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "으앗! 왜, 왜그래!?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……！！\nShannon……차에서 내리렴.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "...녀석들이다...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "아빠...?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "빨리 내려!\n그리고 잘 들으렴. 지금 당장 집으로 돌아가, 알겠지?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "차문"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["學生 A"], "content": "Shannon，拜拜～下週見喔。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "嗯！下週見！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "汽車引擎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon，要搭便車嗎？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "爸！？你在這裡做什麼啊！？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真是的，別再開管理局的車來載我了啦！同學都會笑耶。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "我不放心啊，最近這一區治安也越來越差了……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "那不是都是因為爸沒做好工作？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "哈哈……好吧，我認罪。\n不過，太好了，看到妳在學校有那麼多朋友。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "我早就過了那個老是被欺負的年紀啦，爸別老是只記得那時候的事，我不是小孩子了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "說起來當時真的……要感謝 Simon 啊。\n最近還有再見到他嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "嗯！他很好，也常常找我去看他們練團或表演；他們的樂團很棒，團員也都是很有趣的人喔！特別是 Cherry 姐！他們好像在交……啊！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "交？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "沒……沒事！總之下次爸也去聽吧！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "我哪有那麼多閒時間啊……不就是些吵死人的音樂而已嗎？\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["CP_velkinta", "音樂播放"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "哇！妳幹嘛！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "啊，好巧喔，一打開就是吵死人的音樂耶。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "要不是你送他吉他，他也不會跑去玩樂團囉。我說你們也差不多該解除冷戰了吧？\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……哼，他如果想回來隨時可以回來啊。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "又來了～你這個態度誰想跟你住……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "煞車"], "content": ""}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "哇！怎、怎麼了！？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "……！！\nShannon……下車。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "是那傢伙……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "爸……？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "快下車！聽好，直接回家，知道嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Door_Car", "車門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_04"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Audio_53St._696_05_10]</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["学生 A"], "content": "Shannon，拜拜～下周见喔。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "嗯！下周见！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Car_Stop", "汽车引擎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Kyle"], "content": "Shannon，要搭便车吗？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "爸！ ？你在这里做什么啊！ ？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切换讯号]</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Shannon"], "content": "真是的，别再开管理局的车来载我了啦！同学都会笑耶。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversati